                                             Table "public.topics"
       Column        |            Type             | Collation | Nullable |              Default               
---------------------+-----------------------------+-----------+----------+------------------------------------
 id                  | integer                     |           | not null | nextval('topics_id_seq'::regclass)
 author_id           | integer                     |           |          | 
 created_at          | timestamp without time zone |           | not null | now()
 description         | character varying(123)      |           | not null | 
 title               | character varying(30)       |           | not null | 
 role                | character varying(50)       |           | not null | 
 pending_for_teacher | boolean                     |           |          | 
Indexes:
    "topics_pkey" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)
Foreign-key constraints:
    "topics_author_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (author_id) REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE SET NULL
Referenced by:
    TABLE "posts" CONSTRAINT "posts_topic_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (topic_id) REFERENCES topics(id)

